<TITLE> 7 promoted to secy; 3 made OSDs </TITLE>
<TEXT>
 Dhaka, Jan 25 (bdnews24.com)  Seven additional secretaries have been promoted to secretary, while the telecom secretary and additional home secretary have been made OSDs on Sunday, establishment ministry sources said on Sunday. Eight additional secretaries were also shuffled and 10 joint secretaries transferred. The seven newly promoted secretaries are: ASM Ali Kabir  establishment, Abu Taher Khandaker M Ismail  education, Abdus Sobhan Sikder  shipping, Wahedunnabi Chowhury  power, Najmul Huda Khan  science and information technology, ABM Nuruzzaman - parliament secretariat and Kamrul Alam Rabbani - managing director of Bangladesh Shipping Corporation. The secretaries made OSDs are posts and telecom secretary Dr M Mahbubur Rahman additional home secretary Dr Sheikh Abdur Rashid, as well as PSC secretary M Mukhlesur Rahman. Five secretaries and two additional secretaries have been made OSDs in the past 19 days since the government took office on Jan. 6, including education secretary Mamtazul Islam, health secretary AMM Nasiruddin, jute and textile secretary MA Rashid Sarker and land secretary Abu M Moniruzzaman. bdnews24.
